00:12:34.030 --> 00:12:36.970
They follow entrepreneurs, like
Elon Musk and Gary Vaynerchuk

00:12:36.970 --> 00:12:40.390
and Peter Thiel and
Mark Cuban and Tim Cook.

00:12:40.390 --> 00:12:43.750
And perhaps, like the
