The fact that an entrepreneur
came out with a shoe

00:14:03.280 --> 00:14:06.490
and sold it out to kids
in seconds is unreal.

00:14:06.490 --> 00:14:09.430
High schoolers are paying more
and more attention to esports

00:14:09.430 --> 00:14:10.390
and so is the world.

